We need to prove `LocallyIntegrable (RCLike.ofReal ∘ NNReal.toReal ∘ f) μ` given `hf : @MeasureTheory.MemLorentz α NNReal m0 instENormedSpaceNNReal.toENorm NNReal.instTopologicalSpace f p 1 μ`.

